  "text": "Is there anything with respect to the present spiritual or metaphysical condition or physical condition of this house that we're contemplating that Ra could tell us about that would be deleterious to the instrument's health? I am Ra. We may speak to this subject only to note that there are mechanical electrical devices which control humidity. The basement level is one location, the nature of which is much like that which you have experienced at the basement level of your previous domicile. Less humid conditions would remove the opportunity for the growth of those spores to which the instrument has sensitivity. The upper portions of the domicile are almost, in every case, at acceptable levels of humidity.",
